{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give HGV Drivers a 6 month exemption from CPC through Covid-19 Crisis",
        "additional_details": "Due to social distancing many training companies are unable to offer CPC courses.  By allowing a 6 month exemption to CPC we can enable new, current or retired HGV Drivers to legally obtain HGV jobs during the Covid-19 crisis.  Not only would this be a benefit for the individual but also to the industry.",
        "background": "I would like to propose all drivers who hold a Valid HGV Driving Licence be allowed to drive either without initial CPC entitlement or expired CPC entitlement for a 6 month period.",
